# Utils Directory Structure

The `src/utils` directory contains utility functions and helpers used throughout the project.

- [solana.ts](mdc:src/utils/solana.ts): Solana blockchain-related utilities.
- [transaction.ts](mdc:src/utils/transaction.ts): Functions for handling transactions.
- [feeEstimator.ts](mdc:src/utils/feeEstimator.ts): Functions for estimating transaction fees.
- [index.ts](mdc:src/utils/index.ts): Main export or aggregation file for utilities.

## Usage
- Add new files here for additional utility functions.
- Import and use utilities from this directory in your codebase.
